'''美国体操队性侵丑闻'''是有關[[美國|美國]]女性[[體操|體操]]隊員遭受[[性侵|性侵]]（許多人被性侵時還未成年）的事件，事件從1990年代末開始。有超過368個隊員指控曾被「全國各地的體育館負責人、体操教練、体操相關工作人員」性侵<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/gvqm7y/skandal-u-americkoj-gimnastici-deca-zlostavljana-20-godina|title=New Report Reveals 20-Year Sex Abuse Scandal Across US Gymnastics Programs|last=Messman|first=Lauren|date=2016-12-15|publisher=Vice|language=en|access-date=2018-02-17|quote=At least 368 child gymnasts have alleged sexual assault by gym owners, coaches, and staff working for top gymnastics programs across the country over the last 20 years.}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indystar.com/story/news/2016/12/15/20-year-toll-368-gymnasts-allege-sexual-exploitation/95198724/|title=A 20-year toll: 368 gymnasts allege sexual exploitation|year=2016|publisher=The Indianapolis Star|language=en|access-date=2018-02-17|author=Tim Evans, Mark Alesia and Marisa Kwiatkowski|quote=At least 368 gymnasts have alleged some form of sexual abuse at the hands of their coaches, gym owners and other adults working in gymnastics. That's a rate of one every 20 days. And it's likely an undercount.}}</ref>。其中，有上百個体操隊員的訴訟是針對長期擔任美國體操代表隊隊醫的[[拉里·纳萨尔|拉里·纳萨尔]]，指稱他以提供醫療為理由，性侵至少14年的時間。此一醜聞最早是由[[印第安纳波利斯星报|印第安纳波利斯星报]]在2016年9月報導，受害人超過265名女性<ref name = "hundreds">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-42894833|title=Larry Nassar case: USA Gymnastics doctor 'abused 265 girls'|work=BBC News|date=2018-01-31}}</ref>，包括前{{le|美國女子體操代表隊|United States women's national gymnastics team}}隊員{{le|潔西卡·霍華德|Jessica Howard}}、{{le|傑米·丹茨徹|Jamie Dantzscher}}、[[摩根·懷特|摩根·懷特]]（Morgan White）、{{le|珍妮特·安托林|Jeanette Antolin}}、[[麦凯拉·马罗尼|麦凯拉·马罗尼]]、[[亚历山德拉·莱斯曼|亚历山德拉·莱斯曼]]、{{le|梅姬·尼科爾斯|Maggie Nichols (gymnast)}}、[[加布丽埃勒·道格拉斯|加布丽埃勒·道格拉斯]]、[[西蒙·拜爾斯|西蒙·拜爾斯]]、[[乔婷·韦伯|乔婷·韦伯]]、{{le|薩布麗娜·維加|Sabrina Vega}}、{{le|阿什頓·洛克利爾|Ashton Locklear}}、{{le|凱拉·羅斯|Kyla Ross}}、[[麦迪逊·科齐安|麦迪逊·科齐安]]、{{le|阿曼達·傑特|Amanda Jetter}}、{{le|塔莎·施維克特|Tasha Schwikert}}、{{le|瑪蒂·拉爾森|Mattie Larson}}、{{le|貝利·奇|Bailie Key}}、{{le|肯尼迪·貝克|Kennedy Baker}}、{{le|阿莉莎·鮑曼|Alyssa Baumann}}和{{le|泰林·漢弗萊|Terin Humphrey}}都指控曾受到拉里·纳萨尔的性侵。這是運動史上最大的性侵丑闻<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/19/sports/olympics/nassar-gymnastics-raisman.html|title=Who Has U.S.A. Gymnastics' Back at This Point? The U.S.O.C., for Some Reason|work=The New York Times|date=2018-01-19|first=Juliet|last=Macur}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://time.com/5113091/usa-gymnastics-board-members-resignation-larry-nassar/|title=USA Gymnastics Board Members Resign Amid Larry Nassar Sexual Abuse Scandal|work=Time|date=2018-01-22|first=Alice|last=Park}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2017/dec/16/gymnastics-larry-nassar-sexual-abuse|title=Why don't we care about the biggest sex abuse scandal in sports history?|work=The Guardian|date=2017-12-16|first=Bryan Armen|last=Graham}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2017/11/29/michigan-state-accused-covering-up-worst-sex-abuse-scandal-in-us-sports.html|title=Michigan State accused of covering up worst sex abuse scandal in US sports|work=Fox News|first=Caleb|last=Parke|date=2017-11-30}}</ref>。

拉里·纳萨尔在2017年7月11日針對聯邦提出持有兒童色情製品的指控認罪，在2017年12月7日宣判，有期徒刑60年。同年11月22日，針對州法院提出的七項一級性侵指控認罪，一週後又對另外三項性侵指控認罪。2018年1月24日，拉里·纳萨尔被判刑，刑期至少增加40年，此一刑期是從兒童色情製品的60年服刑期滿開始計算。在2018年2月5日時，拉里·纳萨尔的刑期至少再增加40年。2019年時，拉里·纳萨尔在{{le|美國科爾曼監獄|United States Penitentiary, Coleman}}服刑。

[[印第安纳波利斯星报|印第安纳波利斯星报]]花了九個月調查此事，發現這類性侵普遍的原因是「性掠奪的教練從一個體育館到另一個體育館，寬鬆的監督系統沒有察覺到這些事，或是被這些體育館忽略了這些危險的資訊。」<ref name="TIS2016"/>。美國體操協會（USAG）以及[[密西根州立大學|密西根州立大學]]（拉里·纳萨尔曾在密西根州立大學擔任{{le|骨科醫師|osteopathic physician}}，故該大學也被指控助長拉里·纳萨尔的性侵行為<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nbcchicago.com/news/national-international/Larry-Nassar-Fallout-Michigan-State-US-Olympic-Committee-USA-Gymnastics-470969223.html|title=Michigan State President Resigns; US Olympic Committee Face Fallout of Larry Nassar Sentencing|work=NBC Chicago|date=2018-01-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.latimes.com/nation/la-na-nassar-accountability-20180124-story.html|title=Michigan State University president resigns amid widening calls for accountability over Larry Nassar abuse scandal|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2018-01-24|first=Matt|last=Pearce}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2018/01/15/us/larry-nassar-gymnastics-me-too-sentence/index.html|title=Larry Nassar's sexual abuse victims finally get their days in court|work=CNN|date=2018-01-15|first=Eric|last=Levenson}}</ref>），在前體操運動員提出對拉里·纳萨尔的許多訴訟中，美國體操協會和密西根州立大學也名列被告<ref name=chicagotri>{{cite web|url=https://www.chicagotribune.com/sports/international/ct-usa-gymnastics-fbi-doctor-abuse-20170216-story.html|title=USA Gymnastics alerted FBI in 2015 to doctor accused of abuse|work=Chicago Tribune|date=2017-02-16|first1=Rick|last1=Maese|first2=Will|last2=Hobson}}</ref><ref name=nytsteve>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/03/16/sports/steve-penny-resigns-as-usa-gymnastics-president.html|title=Steve Penny Resigns as U.S.A. Gymnastics President|work=The New York Times|date=2017-03-16|first=John|last=Branch}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/09/14/sports/olympics/sexual-abuse-charges-put-shadow-on-us-gymnastics-federation.html|title=Sexual Abuse Charges Put Shadow on U.S. Gymnastics Federation|work=The New York Times|date=2016-09-13|first=Juliet|last=Macur}}</ref>。除了拉里·纳萨尔外，其他密西根州、賓州、加州、羅德島、印第安那州等地的體操教練也有性侵情形<ref name="TIS2016">{{cite web|url=https://www.indystar.com/story/news/2016/12/15/20-year-toll-368-gymnasts-allege-sexual-exploitation/95198724/|title=A 20-year toll: 368 gymnasts allege sexual exploitation|year=2016|publisher=The Indianapolis Star|language=en|access-date=2018-02-17|author=Tim Evans, Mark Alesia and Marisa Kwiatkowski}}</ref>。

2018年5月16日時，ESPN宣佈受害人獲得{{le|亞瑟·阿什勇氣獎|Arthur Ashe Courage Award}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.si.com/olympics/2018/05/16/larry-nassar-victims-arthur-ashe-award-espy|title=Larry Nassar Sexual Assault Survivors to Receive Arthur Ashe Award For Courage At ESPYs|work=Sports Illustrated|date=2018-05-16}}</ref>。同年的12月13日，美國的[[國家大學體育協會|國家大學體育協會]]（NCAA）頒給梅姬·尼科爾斯{{le|NCAA激勵獎|NCAA Inspiration Award}}，因為梅姬·尼科爾斯是首先舉報拉里·纳萨尔的人<ref>{{cite press release|url=https://www.ncaa.org/about/resources/media-center/news/2019-ncaa-inspiration-award-maggie-nichols |title=2019 NCAA Inspiration Award: Maggie Nichols |publisher=NCAA |date=2018-12-13 |access-date=2018-12-13}}</ref>{{efn|{{le|Shaquem Griffin|Shaquem Griffin}}只有一隻手，在中佛羅里達大學美式足球隊表現出色，也獲得該年的NCAA激勵獎<ref>{{cite press release|url=https://www.ncaa.org/about/resources/media-center/news/2019-ncaa-inspiration-award-shaquem-griffin |title=2019 NCAA Inspiration Award: Shaquem Griffin |publisher=NCAA |date=2018-12-13 |access-date=2018-12-13}}</ref>}}。

